# =============================================================================
# .gitignore  —  Daily Market Brief
# =============================================================================
# IMPORTANT: some files in this project are tracked ON PURPOSE and must NOT be
# added here:
#   - last_run.json   : the state cache is committed back to the repo each run
#                       (spec 5.5 / 8.3). It is the anti-auto-disable mechanism.
#   - runs/           : per-run structured JSON dumps are committed for auditing
#                       (spec 5.6 / 8). Prune to ~90 days, do not ignore.
#   - config.yaml     : tracked (watchlist is low-stakes plaintext; recipient is
#                       a GitHub Secret, not config). See spec 13.
#   - data/*.yaml     : tier_one_calendar.yaml and mechanical_moves.yaml are
#                       source data and must be tracked.
# Secrets never live in the repo at all; they are GitHub Secrets / env vars.
# =============================================================================

# --- Secrets / local env (never commit) ---
.env
.env.*
*.env
secrets.*
*.pem

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.Python
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
.eggs/

# --- Virtual environments ---
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/

# --- Local build output from `python brief.py --no-send` ---
# The no-send build writes preview HTML and any scratch charts to disk for
# inspection. Keep these local-only. Point the no-send output here (e.g. a
# `preview/` dir or a `*.preview.html` name) so test builds never get committed.
preview/
out/
*.preview.html
brief_preview.html

# --- Tooling / caches ---
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~

# Design redesign references — KEEP the approved template + preview harness
# (design-preview/*.j2 and *.py) tracked so the look + preview loop survive across
# chats. Ignore only the GENERATED scratch (rendered HTML + screenshots).
design-preview/*.html
design-preview/*.png
Screenshot *.png
daily_market_brief_claude_design.html
